The paper discusses the representation, management, and analysis of big data, which are key topics in the database (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The paper also explores the relationship between big data and knowledge, which is a topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the infrastructure required for big data management and analysis, which is a topic in cyber infrastructure (cs.CY).
